### GET available vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### GET shipments with status InTransit
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### GET all shipments for a specific customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=customer_ID eq 'c3333333-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'

### POST a new shipment booking
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
  "customer_ID": "c3333333-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "driver_ID": "d2222222-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "vehicle_ID": "v1111111-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "pickupAddress": "10 Link Road",
  "deliveryAddress": "55 Anna Salai",
  "pickupCity": "Mumbai",
  "deliveryCity": "Chennai",
  "weight": 250.00,
  "status": "Booked",
  "bookedAt": "2024-06-11T10:00:00",
  "estimatedDelivery": "2024-06-15",
  "charges": 5000.00,
  "paymentStatus": "Pending"
}

### PATCH shipment status to Delivered
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments(s5555555-0000-0000-0000-000000000002)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Delivered",
  "deliveredAt": "2024-06-08T19:00:00"
}

### GET routes between two cities
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Mumbai' and toCity eq 'Delhi'

### GET drivers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc